 * It registers an event-time timer for the window end and fires when the watermark passes that
 * time.
 *
 * <p>This trigger is designed to work with {@link
 * org.apache.flink.streaming.api.windowing.assigners.PricingSessionWindow} and supports window
 * merging for overlapping trading sessions.
 *
